title: Canada retail e-commerce sales growth 2018 to 2023
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Year-over-year change. In total the number of data points it has is 6.
In general Year-over-year change has fallen over the Year.
Year-over-year change is roughly constant from 2018 to 2020, and finally slightly decreasing from 2020 to 2023.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2021 and 2022.
Maximum Year-over-year change, about 10.1 was reported at Year 2019
Minimum Year-over-year change about 3.1 was reached at Year 2023
